1. *Gladan* sam već dva sata. (I've been hungry for two hours.)
2. Dete je bilo *gladno*. (The child was hungry.)
3. Ne osećam se *gladno*. (I don't feel hungry.)
4. On je *gladan*. (He is hungry.)
5. Ona je zaista *gladna*. (She is really hungry.)
6. Deca su bila *gladna*. (The children were hungry.)